cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.MM 

This paper is primarily focused on computer vision and image analysis, specifically on detecting human-object interactions. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper proposes a new trainable reasoning mechanism, which could fall under the category of cs.RO (Robotics and Control) or cs.MM (Multimedia).
